snippet.title: Amber Heard FIRED From Aquaman 2 After Lying About Donations To Charity's
snippet.description:
Amber Heard FIRED From Aquaman 2 After Lying On Donations To Charity's
And back and forth we go once again! It seemed as though Amber Heard was going to get victory after victory after victory since things started to go her way last November via the Libel case loss of her ex-husband Johnny Depp. However, Depp refused to give up and as a result, he's been pushing new angles to try and get proof that Heard has been lying to the world about the alleged abused that he was said to have done to her. And now, he's gotten a key ruling that might just swing things in his favor for once. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video  and subscribe to the channel!
